name: Russian doll bracelet
description:
This is absolutely gorgeous!

This charming bracelet features 10 vibrant aqua beads with a floral print on, threaded on to elastic with a beautiful russian doll to complete this piece. Its nice and chunky, but not to big. 

Hand-made, unique and beautiful.

P.S. click to enlarge :) xx

name: Keep you by my heart locket
description:
Adorable and unique!

This beautiful locket features a rose cameo, and inside there's space for a picture of you and the person you want closet to your heart. You'll love wearing this, so treat yourself or buy it for someone special.

Perfect for best-friends, your valentine or even for yourself.

P.S click the image to enlarge :) xx

name: Lucky in Love bracelet
description:
This sweet bracelet is the absolute perfect gift for your valentines. If you dont have anybody to treat this year, why not treat yourself to this beautiful piece.

Eachof the 3 pendants are gorgeous, a love key, a love heart and a beautiful bird. 

Unique, handmade and super cute--your new 'everyday' bracelet!

P.S click the image to enlage :) xx

name: Vibrant floral bracelet
description:
This has to be one of the best bracelets on offer, it features vibrant red and blue floral patterned beads on nice stretchy electic, so 'one size fits all'.

I personally have one myself, its a bit different though, so i know its perfect to wear everyday and recieves tonnes of compliments. Its eye-catching, unique and fashionable.

You could give is as a gift, or keep it for yourself :)
